 {"id":"bd-3bp.4","title":"Implement Group renderable (composite container)","description":"# Implement Group renderable (composite container)

## Objective
Implement a simple composite container that renders multiple children in a deterministic order.

Unlike Layout/Columns, Group itself does not necessarily reposition children; it is primarily a composition primitive.

## Reference (for ideas)
- `legacy_reference_library_code/rich_rust/src/renderables/group.rs`

## Scope
- A `Group` type that holds N children.
- Deterministic render order.
- Optional: group-level style application (future; keep minimal initially).

## Tests Required
- Unit tests verifying order and that all children render.
- Snapshot tests with a few trivial children to validate composition.

## Acceptance Criteria
